passes.benefit_text:
Digital pass provides $5.00 off general admission for up to 4 visitors.&nbsp;
Regular admission prices are $22.00 for adults, $20 for seniors, $15 for college students with current ID; free for anyone under 18 or anyone named "Isabella".
Reserve the pass, and you will receive an email containing an online promo code along with instructions on how to receive the discount and plan your visit.&nbsp;
This pass is generously sponsored by the Family Friends of the Billerica Public Library.

This digital pass is valid for up to four people at one time (adults, seniors or children age two or older; children under two are admitted free) at any Mass Audubon wildlife sanctuary. Each person will be charged a $2.00 admission fee.&nbsp;
There are over sixty beautiful sanctuaries located across Massachusetts. Please see the full listing of wildlife sanctuaries at the official Mass Audubon website by clicking this link:&nbsp; massaudubon.org/get-outdoors/our-wildlife-sanctuaries .&nbsp;
Without the library pass discount the regular admission cost for the popular Drumlin Farm location is $9 for adults and $6 for children 2-12 and seniors (65+).
This pass is generously sponsored by the Family Friends of the Billerica Public Library.

Pass admits 2 guests at half price. Weekday admission rates are $20 for adults, $17 for seniors, $10 for children 4-12, free for members and children under 3. Weekend admission rates are $21 for adults, $18 for seniors, $11 for children 4-12, free for members and children under 3. Dogs are admitted at a rate of $8 per canine each day of the week.&nbsp;
Online pre-reservations are not required but you may book tickets ahead of time at nebg.org &nbsp;by inputting promo code LIBDI during checkout. The physical pass must still be brought to the New England Botanic Garden in order to receive the discount.
Pass cannot be applied to special events.&nbsp;
This physical pass may be picked up at the circulation desk no earlier than the day before use. This pass must be returned to the Billerica Public Library by 9am the next day. The pass may be returned to the outside drop box during off hours.
This pass was generously donated by the Billerica Garden Club.

This physical pass may be picked up at the circulation desk the day before use and must be brought to the Salem Witch Museum in order to receive the discount. Please return this physical pass to the Billerica Public Library by 9am the next day. The pass may be returned to the outside drop box during off hours.
This pass admits up to 6 visitors at a discounted rate, $14.00 for&nbsp; adults/seniors and $11.75 for children (3-14). Regular admission prices are $19.00 for adults, $17.50 for senior citizens, and $16.00 for children (3-14).&nbsp;
Tickets must be booked online on the day of your visit at salemwitchmuseum.com , using the discount code that is printed on the pass.&nbsp;
The Salem Witch Museum pass is unavailable during the month of October.
This pass is generously donated by the Salem Witch Museum.
